# Generated per-lesson stub HTMLs (created by scripts/build_lesson_pages.py).
# On Vercel they're written into site/phases/ during build. Locally they
# end up in source phases/ via the site/phases symlink — gitignore so they
# don't clutter the working tree.
phases/[0-9][0-9]-*/[0-9][0-9]-*/index.html
